@Astug
Go to "Settings", under "Options" select "Notifications".
Click on "Settings" on the right of "Enable Events Notifications".
Go under "Important Notifications".
Uncheck "License Validity . . ."

@kzrockz
Turn Norton's "Insight Protection", "Antivirus", "Antispyware", "SONAR Protection".
Restore the file.
Go to Norton "Settings".
Under "Computer Settings", look for "Exclusions", click "Configure" on the right of "Scan Exclusions".
Add your file directory (browse it), on both Scan and Real Time exclusions.
